first we need to label a node
```
kubectl label nodes <nodename> key=value
kubectl label nodes node01 size=small
```

now that we have label the node we can assig node-selector

---
apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: nginx
  labels:
    env: test
spec:
  containers:
  - name: nginx
    image: nginx
    imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent
  nodeSelector:
    size: small
